name: Inception
description:
Inception - is part of Iurie
Belegurschi’s genesis NFT collection
“New World” Iurie trained AI with
hundreds of his Iceland Highlands
photographs taken in the last 15 years
to create a New World in the
Metaverse, the algorithms created a
new and unique dreamlike
landscape.... a New World ... The result
is a unique artwork created from a
collaboration between a machine and
a human. The collector of Inception
will join Iurie on a 5 Day private tour in
Iceland to discover the places he
photographed to create this piece.
